### Open a checking account
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "accountType": "CHECKING",
  "currency": "ZAR",
  "initialDeposit": 1000.00
}

### Open a savings account
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "accountType": "SAVINGS",
  "currency": "ZAR",
  "initialDeposit": 5000.00
}

### Get account by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get accounts for customer
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/customer/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Deposit money
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Idempotency-Key: dep-001

{
  "amount": 2500.00,
  "reference": "Salary deposit"
}

### Withdraw money
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Idempotency-Key: wd-001

{
  "amount": 500.00,
  "reference": "ATM withdrawal"
}

### Freeze account (admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/freeze
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

### Close account (admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/close
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
